Ruben Gallego</b>, <b>Bob Casey</b>, and <b>Tammy Baldwin</b> are more popu=
lar than Biden.<br/><br/>Another possibility? There might be voters who cas=
t votes for their party in Senate, House, and local races, but leave the to=
